    <string name="legal_terms_title">Terms and Conditions</string>
    <string name="legal_last_updated">Last updated: January 2025</string>
    <string name="legal_privacy_1_title">1. Data Controller</string>
    <string name="legal_privacy_1_body">SOZOLAB S.L. is the entity responsible for processing the personal data collected through the Zampa application.</string>
    <string name="legal_privacy_2_title">2. Data We Collect</string>
    <string name="legal_privacy_2_body">We collect the data you provide when you sign up (name, email address, phone number), app usage data, your approximate location to show nearby restaurants (only while the app is in use and with your permission), and the device token for sending push notifications.</string>
    <string name="legal_privacy_3_title">3. Purpose of Processing</string>
    <string name="legal_privacy_3_body">We use your data to:\n• Manage your account and authentication.\n• Show you nearby dining offers.\n• Send you notifications about new menus from your favorite restaurants (only if you allow it).\n• Improve the service through aggregated and anonymous analysis.</string>
    <string name="legal_privacy_4_title">4. Legal Basis</string>
    <string name="legal_privacy_4_body">Processing is based on the performance of the contract for use of the application (Art. 6.1.b GDPR) and, in the case of push notifications, on your explicit consent (Art. 6.1.a GDPR).</string>
    <string name="legal_privacy_5_title">5. Data Retention</string>
    <string name="legal_privacy_5_body">We retain your data as long as your account remains active. You can request the deletion of your account and data at any time.</string>
    <string name="legal_privacy_6_title">6. Your Rights</string>
    <string name="legal_privacy_6_body">You have the right to access, rectify, delete, restrict, or object to the processing of your data, as well as the right to data portability. You can exercise these rights by writing to soporte@getzampa.com.</string>
    <string name="legal_privacy_7_title">7. Contact</string>
    <string name="legal_privacy_7_body">For any privacy-related inquiries, write to us at soporte@getzampa.com.</string>
    <string name="legal_terms_1_title">1. Acceptance of Terms</string>
    <string name="legal_terms_1_body">By using Zampa you accept these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree, do not use the application.</string>
    <string name="legal_terms_2_title">2. Description of Service</string>
    <string name="legal_terms_2_body">Zampa is a platform that connects hospitality businesses (\"merchants\") with customers looking for daily menu deals and special dishes. Merchants are responsible for the accuracy of their listings.</string>
    <string name="legal_terms_3_title">3. Registration and Accounts</string>
    <string name="legal_terms_3_body">You must be at least 16 years old to sign up. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your password. Notify us immediately if you detect unauthorized use of your account.</string>
    <string name="legal_terms_4_title">4. Merchant Content</string>
    <string name="legal_terms_4_body">Prices, descriptions, schedules, and menu availability are the sole responsibility of each merchant. Zampa does not guarantee the availability of any published offer.</string>
    <string name="legal_terms_5_title">5. Acceptable Use</string>
    <string name="legal_terms_5_body">The following is prohibited:\n• Publishing false or misleading information.\n• Using the platform for illegal activities.\n• Attempting to access other users\' data.\n• Scraping or automating mass access to the platform.</string>
    <string name="legal_terms_6_title">6. Intellectual Property</string>
    <string name="legal_terms_6_body">The design, code, and brand of Zampa are the property of SOZOLAB S.L. Content published by merchants (photos, descriptions) is the property of their respective owners.</string>
    <string name="legal_terms_7_title">7. Limitation of Liability</string>
